quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  40,69,"E a tinaali, …ďen yeddondirtee…ďe e Aayeeje Allah …óen, ko honno …ďe firlitoraa"
  40,70,"∆Āen fennu…ďe Deftere nden, e kon ko Men nuliri Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen; …ďe aray anndude"
  40,71,"tuma kolombooje …óen wa…óoyaa e daa…óe ma…ď…ďe, e jolokooje(callalle) …óen, hara hi…ďe daasiree"
  40,72,ka nder wul…óam; refti …ďe hu…ď…ďoyee ka nder Yiite
  40,73,"Refti …ďe wi'anee: \"Ko honto woni …óin …ói kafidayno…óon"
  40,74,"Ko aldah e Allah?\" ∆Āe wi'a: \"∆äi majjitike men. Wurin, men wonaano ko adii, e rewugol hay huunde\". Ko hona nih Allah majjinirta heefer…ďe …ďen"
  40,75,"Ko wa…ói on …óum, ko ko weltorayno…óon kon ka hoore leydi, ko aldaa e goonga, e ko wewlirayno…óon kon"
  40,76,"Naatiree dame Jahannama …óen, luttugol ton. Nge bonii jaa∆īorde wonande mawnintinii…ďe …ďen"
  40,77,"Mu√Ī√Īo. Pellet, fodoore Allah nden, ko goonga. Ko si Men hollete yoga e ko Men fodi …ďe kon, maa hara Men ∆īettite (ado mun) ko ka Amen …ďe ruttirtee"
  40,78,"Gom…óii Men imminii Nulaa…ďe ado maa. Hino e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Men sifani maa fii mun; hino ma…ď…ďe, …ďe Men sifanaaki ma fii mun. Haananaa Nulaa…óo, addugol Aaya, si wanaa e duŇčayee Allah. Si yamiroore Allah nden arii, goonga √Īaawirte meerente'en sooya nden √Īalnde"